Inside Out;;89;;98;;PG;;Riley (Kaitlyn Dias) is a happy, hockey-loving 11-year-old Midwestern girl, but her world turns upside-down when she and her parents move to San Francisco. Riley's emotions -- led by Joy (Amy Poehler) -- try to guide her through this difficult, life-changing event. However, the stress of the move brings Sadness (Phyllis Smith) to the forefront. When Joy and Sadness are inadvertently swept into the far reaches of Riley's mind, the only emotions left in Headquarters are Anger, Fear and Disgust.;;Fantasy,Animation,Comedy,Kids & family;;Pete Docter;;2015;;Amy Poehler,Phyllis Smith,Richard Kind,Bill Hader,Lewis Black,Mindy Kaling,Kaitlyn Dias,Diane Lane,Kyle MacLachlan;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inside_out_2015